hadiths[15]{hadithnumber,text}:
990,"aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se raat mein Namaz ke mutaalliq malum kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raat ki Namaz 2-2 rakaat hai phir jab koi subah ho janey se darey to aik rakaat padh ley , wo uski saari Namaz ko taaq bana degi."
991,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) witr ki jab teen rakatein padhtey to 2 rakaat padh kar salam phertey yahan tak ke zarurat se baat bhi kartey.
992,"aap aik raat apni khala Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan soey (aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke) mein takiya ke chaudaan mein let gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ki biwi lambai mein letein , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey jab aadhi raat guzar gaee ya iske lagbhag to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey neend ke asar ko chehra Mubarak par hath pher kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne door kya. iske baad aale-Imraan ki 10 aayatein padhein. phir aik puraanii mashk pani ki bhari hui latak rahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas gaey aur achi tarah wuzu kya aur Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey. maine bhi aisa hi kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) piyaar se apna daahinaa hath mere sar rakh kar aur mera kaan pakad kar usey malney lagey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat , phir 2 rakaat , phir 2 rakaat , phir 2 rakaat , phir 2 rakaat sab baara rakatein phir aik rakaat witr padh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) let gaey, yahan tak ke muazzan subah sadiq ki itlaa dene aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir khadey ho kar do rakaat sunnat Namaz padhi. phir bahar tashrif laey aur subah ki Namaz padhai."
993,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, raat ki Namaz 2-2 rakatein hain aur jab to khatm karna chahey to aik rakaat witr padh ley jo saari Namaz ko taaq bana degi. Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke ham ne bahut son ko teen rakaat witr padhtey bhi paya hai aur teen ya aik ( rakaat witr ( sab jaaiz hai aur mujh ko ummeed hai ke kisi mein qabahat na hogi."
994,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) gyara (11) rakatein ( witr aur tahajjud ki) padhtey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki yahi Namaz thi. murad unki raat ki Namaz thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sajda un rakaton mein itna lamba hota tha ke sar uthaney se pahley tum mein se koi shakhs bhi pachaas aayatein padh sakta aur fajr ki Namaz farz se pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sunnat 2 rakatein padhtey they iske baad) zara der ( daahiney pahlu par let rahtey yahan tak ke azan dene wala bulaney ke liye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aataa."
995,Namaz subah se pahley ki 2 rakaton ke mutaalliq aap ka kya khayal hai? kya main unmein lambi qirat kar sakta hoon? unhon-ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to raat ki Namaz ( tahajjud ( 2-2 rakaat karke padhtey they phir aik rakaat padh kar unko taaq bana letey aur subah ki Namaz se pahley ki 2 rakatein ( sunnat fajr to ( is tarah padhtey maano azan ( iqamat ( ki awaz aap ke kaan mein pad rahi hai. Hammad ki us se murad ye hai ke aap jaldi padh letey.
996,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat ke har hisse mein bhi witr padhi hai aur aakhir mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka witr subah ke qareeb pahuncha .
997,aap ne farmaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (tahajjud ki) Namaz padhtey rahtey aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bistar par arz mein leti rahtii. jab witr padhney lagtey to mujhey bhi jaga detey aur main bhi witr padh letii.
998,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke witr raat ki tamam namazon ke baad padha karo.
999,main Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka ke rastey mein tha. Saeed ne kaha ke jab rastey mein mujhey fajr  honey ka khatrah hua to sawari se utar kar maine witr padh liya aur phir Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se ja mila. aap ne puchha ke kahan ruk gaey they? maine kaha ke ab subah ka waqt honey hi wala tha isliye main sawari se utar kar witr padhney laga. is par Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke kya tumharey liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka amal achchha namoona nahi hai. maine arz kya kyon nahi beshak hai. aap ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to oont hi par witr padh liya kartey they.
1000,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar main apni sawari hi par raat ki Namaz isharon se padh letey they chahe sawari ka rukh kisi taraf ho jata Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isharon se padhtey rahtey magar faraaiz is tarah nahi padhtey they aur witr apni ontni par padh letey.
1001,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah ki Namaz mein qunoot padha hai? aap ne farmaya ke haan, phir puchha gaya ke kya rukoo se pahley? to aap ne farmaya ke rukoo ke baad thodey dinon tak."
1002,"maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se qunoot ke barey mein puchha to aap ne farmaya ke duaaey qunoot (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein) padhi jati thi. maine puchha ke rukoo se pahley ya iske ba'd? aap ne farmaya ke rukoo se pahley. Aasim ne kaha ke aap hi ke hawale se falan shakhs ne khabar di hai ke aap ne rukoo ke baad farmaya tha. iska jawab Anas ne ye diya ke unhon-ne ghalat samjhaa. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo ke baad sirf aik mahina duaaey qunoot padhi thi. hua ye tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba mein se 70 qaariyon ke qareeb mushrikon ki aik qaum (banii-Aamir) ki taraf se unko taleem dene ke liye bhejey they, ye log unke siwa they jin par aap ne baddua ki thi. unmein aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan ahad tha, lekin unhon-ne ahad shikanii ki (aur qaariyon ko mar daalaa) to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik maheene tak (rukoo' ke baad) qunoot padhtey rahe un par baddua kartey rahe."
1003,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik maheene tak duaae-qunoot padhi aur is mein qabaayel Ral-w-Zakwan par baddua ki thi.
1004,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein qunoot maghrib aur fajr mein padhi jati thi.
